  <brief_title>Irinotecan in Treating Aging Patients With Solid Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Pharmacology In The Elderly: Prospective Evaluation Of The Pharmacokinetics, Pharmacogenetics And Pharmacodynamics Of CPT-11 And Aging</official_title>
